Lingua::Translate::Google version 0.21
======================================

This module is a wrapper for WWW::Google::Translate
which provides the Google plugin for Lingua::Translate.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Carp
    I18N::LangTags
    Lingua::Translate
    Readonly
    Test::More
    Unicode::MapUTF8

ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
   This module is based on Lingua::Translate::Babelfish by Sam Vilain <enki@snowcra.sh>.

